###
### 8. Retrieve All Enemies
GET {{baseUrl}}/enemies
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###
### 9. Get Specific Enemy (Goblin - adjust ID from response above)
# Replace {id} with actual ID from creation response
GET {{baseUrl}}/enemies/{id}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###
### 10. Update an Enemy (Example: Increase Goblin's Health)
# Replace {id} with actual ID from GET response
PUT {{baseUrl}}/enemies/{id}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Goblin Elite",
  "description": "A stronger variant of the common goblin, with better equipment.",
  "health": 25,
  "attack": 10,
  "defense": 4,
  "experience": 60,
  "drops": [
    {
      "itemName": "Gold",
      "dropRate": 0.9,
      "quantity": 15
    },
    {
      "itemName": "Goblin Dagger",
      "dropRate": 0.6,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

###
### 11. Delete an Enemy (Example: Delete a test enemy)
# Replace {id} with actual ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/enemies/{id}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
